title: Ike Barinholtz on Goodfellas
itunes:title: Ike Barinholtz on Goodfellas
description:
Ike Barinholtz is a very funny actor, and it turns out he's a talented writer and director as well. Chuck sits down with Ike this week to talk about his new movie The Oath, and his movie crush, Goodfellas.
